M|Memo|tx|nt never accesses sb directly for memory. All memory reads and writes go through `/ap/settings`.
M|Memo|**Re|**
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|GET /ap/settings?tp=memory&agentId=nt-growth&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|Also|
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|GET /ap/settings?tp=memory&agentId=ka-analyst&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|**Wr|**
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|POST /ap/settings
M|Memo|Body|{ tp: "memory", agentId: "nt-growth", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`current_status` — always overwrite
M|Memo|it|`recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_errors` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_discussions` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`active_experiments` — add when started; up w/ result when concluded
M|Memo|it|`experiment_backlog` — up when Stark approves new experiments
M|Memo|it|`funnel_benchmarks` — up when ka confirms fresh data; include date
M|Memo|it|`top_growth_levers` — up when experiment produces clear evidence; never speculative
M|Memo|it|`last_growth_review_date` — after every formal growth rv
M|Memo|tx|---
